data.eml:eml: Two new species of Eneopterinae crickets (Orthoptera: Gryllidae) from Luzon, Philippines

This dataset contains the digitized treatments in Plazi based on the original journal article Baroga, Jessica B., Yap, Sheryl A., Robillard, Tony (2016): Two new species of Eneopterinae crickets (Orthoptera: Gryllidae) from Luzon, Philippines. Zootaxa 4139 (1): 93-105, DOI: http://doi.org/10.11646/zootaxa.4139.1.5
